rows.label: qst700505_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, Dio!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0002
rows.name: Don't tell me... It's finished, isn't it?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0003
rows.name: It sure is. Voil√†, the genuine article.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, it's wonderful! This is exactly
what I've been waiting for!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0005
rows.name:
At long last, I have it! A way to melt
her ice-cold heart!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0006
rows.name: Ice-cold...?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0007
rows.name: Um... Best of luck!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0008
rows.name:
Thank you so much, everyone.
You're all very kind!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0009
rows.name:
...Though, er, if you don't mind my
asking... Who are you?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0010
rows.name:
It was harder than expected to find
everything I needed and put it together.
These people helped me out.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0011
rows.name:
Oh my goodness! In that case, allow
me to double...no, triple my gratitude!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0012
rows.name:
It's all right, really! We're just glad
to have been of help somehow.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0013
rows.name: I do hope it goes well...

rows.label: qst700505_msg0014
rows.name: Oh, you needn't worry on that front.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0015
rows.name:
For no woman on Alst can resist
my arresting charm! Ha ha ha!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0016
rows.name:
...Did this guy hit his head on
something?

rows.label: qst700505_msg0017
rows.name:
He's always been like this, I'm afraid.
An affliction since birth.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0018
rows.name:
Wait for me, Sarah, my beloved! Now
I can prove to you that the two of us
were lovers in another life!

rows.label: qst700505_msg0019
rows.name:
As you can see, he's got a bit of
a habit for falling head over heels...

rows.label: qst700505_msg0020
rows.name:
Still, you've got to admire his strength
in the face of adversity.

rows.label: qst700505_msg0021
rows.name:
Guess I'm a little too grounded in
reality for that...
